## Key Patterns Summary

| Pattern | Source | Key Implementation |
|---------|--------|-------------------|
| Category with slug/icon | awesome-chatgpt-prompts | `{ id, name, slug, icon, promptCount }` |
| Hierarchical categories | Joystream | `parentCategoryId` for subcategories |
| Pinned posts per channel | Mattermost | `pinnedPosts: { [channelId]: postId[] }` |
| Sticky thread ordering | MBBS, Joystream | `stickyThreadIds` array on category |
| Featured guides section | llms-txt-hub, GitHub Docs | Separate `featured` flag with grid layout |
| Pin toggle button | awesome-chatgpt-prompts | POST/DELETE to `/api/{id}/pin` endpoint |
| Sort pinned first | nrwl/nx | Separate, sort, then concatenate arrays |
